RPI -- Mainboard : USB (serial, ttyACM0) >
RPI -- GripperCam : USB (webcam, video0)
RPI -- HeadCam :  USB (webcam, video2)
RPI -- HeadSpeaker : USB (geluidskaart RPI, kanaal 1)
RPI -- HeadMic : USB (standaard microfoon)

Mainboard -- Base :  UART (RX/TX) >
Mainboard -- Temperature : I2C (0x4B, p3t1755dpz)
Base -- HillSensor : onewire? (IR sensor) >
Base -- Bump : ? (pressure sensor) >

Mainboard -- ToF_Left : I2C (0x2B, VL53L7CX) >
Mainboard -- ToF_Right : I2C (0x2A, VL53L7CX) >
Mainboard --- Head: I2C (0x5B) >
Mainboard --- Eyes: I2C (0x5A) >
Mainboard --- Arm: I2C (0x5C) >
Arm -- Cobot280 : ? (servo 6-DoF) >
Arm -- Gripper :  onewire (L7805CV via 74lvc1g125gw/74lvc1g126gw 3-state bus driver) >
Head -- Dynamixel : onewire (servo 2-DoF 74lvc1g125gw/74lvc1g126gw 3-state bus driver) >
Eyes -- "2" Eyes_FW : ? >
Eyes -- Mouth : Audio_R (Graphic Equalizer MSGEQ7) >

